Medica Affirms Profit Margin of More Than 26%, Investir Says

-- B y   A l a n   K a t z
-- 
2011-10-22T09:54:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-22/medica-affirms-profit-margin-of-more-than-26-investir-says.html
Medica SA (MDCA) , a French nursing-home
operator, affirmed its target for a profit margin of more than
26 percent this year, the French weekly  Investir  said, citing
Chief Executive Jacques Bailet.  Earnings before interest, taxes, depreciation, amortization
and rental expenses was 26 percent of revenue in the first half
of the year, the company reported in September.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Alan Katz  in Paris at   akatz5@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Melissa Pozsgay at   mpozsgay@bloomberg.net . 